{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"One of my favorite parts"},{"time":2000,"text":"of my job at the Gates Foundation"},{"time":4000,"text":"is that I get to travel to the developing world,"},{"time":6000,"text":"and I do that quite regularly."},{"time":8000,"text":"And when I meet the mothers"},{"time":10000,"text":"in so many of these remote places,"},{"time":12000,"text":"I'm really struck by the things"},{"time":14000,"text":"that we have in common."},{"time":16000,"text":"They want what we want for our children"},{"time":19000,"text":"and that is for their children to grow up successful,"},{"time":22000,"text":"to be healthy, and to have a successful life."},{"time":25000,"text":"But I also see lots of poverty,"},{"time":28000,"text":"and it's quite jarring,"},{"time":31000,"text":"both in the scale and the scope of it."},{"time":33000,"text":"My first trip in India, I was in a person's home"},{"time":36000,"text":"where they had dirt floors, no running water,"},{"time":38000,"text":"no electricity,"},{"time":40000,"text":"and that's really what I see all over the world."},{"time":43000,"text":"So in short, I'm startled by all the things"},{"time":46000,"text":"that they don't have."},{"time":49000,"text":"But I am surprised by one thing that they do have:"},{"time":53000,"text":"Coca-Cola."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"Coke is everywhere."},{"time":57000,"text":"In fact, when I travel to the developing world,"},{"time":59000,"text":"Coke feels ubiquitous."},{"time":61000,"text":"And so when I come back from these trips,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and I'm thinking about development,"},{"time":65000,"text":"and I'm flying home and I'm thinking,"},{"time":67000,"text":"\"We're trying to deliver condoms to people or vaccinations,\""},{"time":70000,"text":"you know, Coke's success kind of stops and makes you wonder:"},{"time":73000,"text":"how is it that they can get Coke"},{"time":75000,"text":"to these far-flung places?"},{"time":77000,"text":"If they can do that,"},{"time":79000,"text":"why can't governments and NGOs do the same thing?"},{"time":82000,"text":"And I'm not the first person to ask this question."},{"time":85000,"text":"But I think, as a community,"},{"time":87000,"text":"we still have a lot to learn."},{"time":90000,"text":"It's staggering, if you think about Coca-Cola."},{"time":92000,"text":"They sell 1.5 billion servings"},{"time":95000,"text":"every single day."},{"time":98000,"text":"That's like every man, woman and child on the planet"},{"time":100000,"text":"having a serving of Coke every week."},{"time":103000,"text":"So why does this matter?"},{"time":106000,"text":"Well, if we're going to speed up the progress"},{"time":109000,"text":"and go even faster"},{"time":111000,"text":"on the set of Millennium Development Goals that we're set as a world,"},{"time":114000,"text":"we need to learn from the innovators,"},{"time":116000,"text":"and those innovators"},{"time":118000,"text":"come from every single sector."},{"time":121000,"text":"I feel that, if we can understand"},{"time":123000,"text":"what makes something like Coca-Cola ubiquitous,"},{"time":126000,"text":"we can apply those lessons then for the public good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131000,"text":"Coke's success is relevant,"},{"time":133000,"text":"because if we can analyze it, learn from it,"},{"time":136000,"text":"then we can save lives."},{"time":138000,"text":"So that's why I took a bit of time to study Coke."},{"time":142000,"text":"And I think there are really three things"},{"time":144000,"text":"we can take away from Coca-Cola."},{"time":146000,"text":"They take real-time data"},{"time":148000,"text":"and immediately feed it back into the product."},{"time":151000,"text":"They tap into local entrepreneurial talent,"},{"time":154000,"text":"and they do incredible marketing."},{"time":157000,"text":"So let's start with the data."},{"time":160000,"text":"Now Coke has a very clear bottom line --"},{"time":162000,"text":"they report to a set of shareholders, they have to turn a profit."},{"time":165000,"text":"So they take the data,"},{"time":167000,"text":"and they use it to measure progress."},{"time":169000,"text":"They have this very continuous feedback loop."},{"time":171000,"text":"They learn something, they put it back into the product,"},{"time":173000,"text":"they put it back into the market."},{"time":175000,"text":"They have a whole team called \"Knowledge and Insight.\""},{"time":177000,"text":"It's a lot like other consumer companies."},{"time":179000,"text":"So if you're running Namibia for Coca-Cola,"},{"time":181000,"text":"and you have a 107 constituencies,"},{"time":183000,"text":"you know where every can versus bottle"},{"time":186000,"text":"of Sprite, Fanta or Coke was sold,"},{"time":188000,"text":"whether it was a corner store,"},{"time":190000,"text":"a supermarket or a pushcart."},{"time":192000,"text":"So if sales start to drop,"},{"time":194000,"text":"then the person can identify the problem"},{"time":196000,"text":"and address the issue."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199000,"text":"Let's contrast that for a minute to development."},{"time":203000,"text":"In development, the evaluation comes"},{"time":206000,"text":"at the very end of the project."},{"time":209000,"text":"I've sat in a lot of those meetings,"},{"time":211000,"text":"and by then,"},{"time":213000,"text":"it is way too late to use the data."},{"time":216000,"text":"I had somebody from an NGO"},{"time":218000,"text":"once describe it to me as bowling in the dark."},{"time":220000,"text":"They said, \"You roll the ball, you hear some pins go down."},{"time":223000,"text":"It's dark, you can't see which one goes down until the lights come on,"},{"time":226000,"text":"and then you an see your impact.\""},{"time":229000,"text":"Real-time data"},{"time":231000,"text":"turns on the lights."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"So what's the second thing that Coke's good at?"},{"time":237000,"text":"They're good at tapping into"},{"time":239000,"text":"that local entrepreneurial talent."},{"time":241000,"text":"Coke's been in Africa since 1928,"},{"time":243000,"text":"but most of the time they couldn't reach the distant markets,"},{"time":246000,"text":"because they had a system that was a lot like in the developed world,"},{"time":249000,"text":"which was a large truck rolling down the street."},{"time":252000,"text":"And in Africa, the remote places,"},{"time":254000,"text":"it's hard to find a good road."},{"time":256000,"text":"But Coke noticed something --"},{"time":258000,"text":"they noticed that local people were taking the product, buying it in bulk"},{"time":261000,"text":"and then reselling it in these hard-to-reach places."},{"time":265000,"text":"And so they took a bit of time to learn about that."},{"time":267000,"text":"And they decided in 1990"},{"time":269000,"text":"that they wanted to start training the local entrepreneurs,"},{"time":271000,"text":"giving them small loans."},{"time":273000,"text":"They set them up as what they called micro-distribution centers,"},{"time":276000,"text":"and those local entrepreneurs then hire sales people,"},{"time":279000,"text":"who go out with bicycles and pushcarts and wheelbarrows"},{"time":282000,"text":"to sell the product."},{"time":284000,"text":"There are now some 3,000 of these centers"},{"time":286000,"text":"employing about 15,000 people in Africa."},{"time":290000,"text":"In Tanzania and Uganda,"},{"time":292000,"text":"they represent 90 percent"},{"time":294000,"text":"of Coke's sales."},{"time":298000,"text":"Let's look at the development side."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300000,"text":"What is it that governments and NGOs"},{"time":302000,"text":"can learn from Coke?"},{"time":304000,"text":"Governments and NGOs"},{"time":306000,"text":"need to tap into that local entrepreneurial talent as well,"},{"time":309000,"text":"because the locals know how to reach"},{"time":311000,"text":"the very hard-to-serve places, their neighbors,"},{"time":314000,"text":"and they know what motivates them to make change."},{"time":318000,"text":"I think a great example of this"},{"time":320000,"text":"is Ethiopia's new health extension program."},{"time":323000,"text":"The government noticed in Ethiopia"},{"time":325000,"text":"that many of the people were so far away from a health clinic,"},{"time":328000,"text":"they were over a day's travel away from a health clinic."},{"time":331000,"text":"So if you're in an emergency situation -- or if you're a mom about to deliver a baby --"},{"time":334000,"text":"forget it, to get to the health care center."},{"time":337000,"text":"They decided that wasn't good enough,"},{"time":339000,"text":"so they went to India and studied the Indian state of Kerala"},{"time":341000,"text":"that also had a system like this,"},{"time":343000,"text":"and they adapted it for Ethiopia."},{"time":345000,"text":"And in 2003, the government of Ethiopia"},{"time":347000,"text":"started this new system in their own country."},{"time":350000,"text":"They trained 35,000 health extension workers"},{"time":353000,"text":"to deliver care directly to the people."},{"time":356000,"text":"In just five years,"},{"time":358000,"text":"their ratio went from one worker for every 30,000 people"},{"time":362000,"text":"to one worker for every 2,500 people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367000,"text":"Now, think about"},{"time":369000,"text":"how this can change people's lives."},{"time":372000,"text":"Health extension workers can help with so many things,"},{"time":375000,"text":"whether it's family planning, prenatal care,"},{"time":378000,"text":"immunizations for the children,"},{"time":380000,"text":"or advising the woman to get to the facility on time"},{"time":383000,"text":"for an on-time delivery."},{"time":386000,"text":"That is having real impact"},{"time":388000,"text":"in a country like Ethiopia,"},{"time":390000,"text":"and it's why you see their child mortality numbers"},{"time":393000,"text":"coming down 25 percent"},{"time":395000,"text":"from 2000 to 2008."},{"time":398000,"text":"In Ethiopia, there are hundreds of thousands of children living"},{"time":401000,"text":"because of this health extension worker program."},{"time":405000,"text":"So what's the next step for Ethiopia?"},{"time":407000,"text":"Well, they're already starting talk about this."},{"time":409000,"text":"They're starting to talk about, \"How do you have the health community workers"},{"time":412000,"text":"generate their own ideas?"},{"time":414000,"text":"How do you incent them based on the impact that they're getting"},{"time":416000,"text":"out in those remote villages?\""},{"time":419000,"text":"That's how you tap into local entrepreneurial talent"},{"time":422000,"text":"and you unlock people's potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"The third component of Coke's success"},{"time":429000,"text":"is marketing."},{"time":431000,"text":"Ultimately, Coke's success"},{"time":433000,"text":"depends on one crucial fact"},{"time":435000,"text":"and that is that people want"},{"time":437000,"text":"a Coca-Cola."},{"time":439000,"text":"Now the reason these micro-entrepreneurs"},{"time":441000,"text":"can sell or make a profit"},{"time":443000,"text":"is they have to sell every single bottle in their pushcart or their wheelbarrow."},{"time":446000,"text":"So, they rely on Coca-Cola"},{"time":449000,"text":"in terms of its marketing,"},{"time":451000,"text":"and what's the secret to their marketing?"},{"time":454000,"text":"Well, it's aspirational."},{"time":456000,"text":"It is associated that product"},{"time":458000,"text":"with a kind of life that people want to live."},{"time":461000,"text":"So even though it's a global company,"},{"time":463000,"text":"they take a very local approach."},{"time":466000,"text":"Coke's global campaign slogan"},{"time":468000,"text":"is \"Open Happiness.\""},{"time":470000,"text":"But they localize it."},{"time":472000,"text":"And they don't just guess what makes people happy;"},{"time":474000,"text":"they go to places like Latin America"},{"time":476000,"text":"and they realize that happiness there"},{"time":478000,"text":"is associated with family life."},{"time":480000,"text":"And in South Africa,"},{"time":482000,"text":"they associate happiness"},{"time":484000,"text":"with seriti or community respect."},{"time":488000,"text":"Now, that played itself out in the World Cup campaign."},{"time":491000,"text":"Let's listen to this song that Coke created for it,"},{"time":493000,"text":"\"Wavin' Flag\" by a Somali hip hop artist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":497000,"text":"(Video) K'Naan: ♫ Oh oh oh oh oh o-oh ♫"},{"time":500000,"text":"♫ Oh oh oh oh oh oh oh oh oh oh ♫"},{"time":504000,"text":"♫ Oh oh oh oh oh o-oh ♫"},{"time":506000,"text":"♫ Oh oh oh oh oh oh oh oh o-oh ♫"},{"time":510000,"text":"♫Give you freedom, give you fire♫"},{"time":513000,"text":"♫ Give you reason, take you higher ♫"},{"time":516000,"text":"♫ See the champions take the field now ♫"},{"time":519000,"text":"♫ You define us, make us feel proud ♫"},{"time":523000,"text":"♫ In the streets our heads are lifted ♫"},{"time":526000,"text":"♫ As we lose our inhibition ♫"},{"time":529000,"text":"♫ Celebration, it's around us ♫"},{"time":532000,"text":"♫ Every nation, all around us ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":536000,"text":"Melinda French Gates: It feels pretty good, right?"},{"time":538000,"text":"Well, they didn't stop there --"},{"time":540000,"text":"they localized it into 18 different languages."},{"time":542000,"text":"And it went number one on the pop chart"},{"time":544000,"text":"in 17 countries."},{"time":547000,"text":"It reminds me of a song that I remember from my childhood,"},{"time":550000,"text":"\"I'd Like to Teach the World to Sing,\""},{"time":553000,"text":"that also went number one on the pop charts."},{"time":556000,"text":"Both songs have something in common:"},{"time":559000,"text":"that same appeal"},{"time":561000,"text":"of celebration and unity."},{"time":565000,"text":"So how does health and development market?"},{"time":568000,"text":"Well, it's based on avoidance,"},{"time":571000,"text":"not aspirations."},{"time":573000,"text":"I'm sure you've heard some of these messages."},{"time":575000,"text":"\"Use a condom, don't get AIDS.\""},{"time":578000,"text":"\"Wash you hands, you might not get diarrhea.\""},{"time":581000,"text":"It doesn't sound anything like \"Wavin' Flag\" to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586000,"text":"And I think we make a fundamental mistake --"},{"time":588000,"text":"we make an assumption,"},{"time":590000,"text":"that we think that, if people need something,"},{"time":592000,"text":"we don't have to make them want that."},{"time":595000,"text":"And I think that's a mistake."},{"time":597000,"text":"And there's some indications around the world that this is starting to change."},{"time":600000,"text":"One example is sanitation."},{"time":603000,"text":"We know that a million and a half children"},{"time":605000,"text":"die a year from diarrhea"},{"time":607000,"text":"and a lot of it is because of open defecation."},{"time":610000,"text":"But there's a solution: you build a toilet."},{"time":613000,"text":"But what we're finding around the world, over and over again,"},{"time":616000,"text":"is, if you build a toilet and you leave it there,"},{"time":619000,"text":"it doesn't get used."},{"time":621000,"text":"People reuse it for a slab for their home."},{"time":623000,"text":"They sometimes store grain in it."},{"time":625000,"text":"I've even seen it used for a chicken coop."},{"time":627000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":629000,"text":"But what does marketing really entail"},{"time":631000,"text":"that would make a sanitation solution get a result in diarrhea?"},{"time":634000,"text":"Well, you work with the community."},{"time":636000,"text":"You start to talk to them about why open defecation"},{"time":638000,"text":"is something that shouldn't be done in the village,"},{"time":640000,"text":"and they agree to that."},{"time":642000,"text":"But then you take the toilet and you position it"},{"time":645000,"text":"as a modern, trendy convenience."},{"time":648000,"text":"One state in Northern India has gone so far"},{"time":650000,"text":"as to link toilets to courtship."},{"time":653000,"text":"And it works -- look at these headlines."},{"time":656000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":660000,"text":"I'm not kidding."},{"time":662000,"text":"Women are refusing to marry men without toilets."},{"time":664000,"text":"No loo, no \"I do.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":667000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":669000,"text":"Now, it's not just a funny headline --"},{"time":672000,"text":"it's innovative. It's an innovative marketing campaign."},{"time":675000,"text":"But more importantly,"},{"time":677000,"text":"it saves lives."},{"time":680000,"text":"Take a look at this --"},{"time":682000,"text":"this is a room full of young men"},{"time":684000,"text":"and my husband, Bill."},{"time":686000,"text":"And can you guess what the young men are waiting for?"},{"time":690000,"text":"They're waiting to be circumcised."},{"time":693000,"text":"Can you you believe that?"},{"time":695000,"text":"We know that circumcision reduces HIV infection"},{"time":698000,"text":"by 60 percent in men."},{"time":700000,"text":"And when we first heard this result inside the Foundation,"},{"time":703000,"text":"I have to admit, Bill and I were scratching our heads a little bit"},{"time":705000,"text":"and we were saying, \"But who's going to volunteer for this procedure?\""},{"time":708000,"text":"But it turns out the men do,"},{"time":710000,"text":"because they're hearing from their girlfriends"},{"time":712000,"text":"that they prefer it,"},{"time":714000,"text":"and the men also believe it improves their sex life."},{"time":718000,"text":"So if we can start to understand"},{"time":721000,"text":"what people really want"},{"time":723000,"text":"in health and development,"},{"time":725000,"text":"we can change communities"},{"time":727000,"text":"and we can change whole nations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731000,"text":"Well, why is all of this so important?"},{"time":734000,"text":"So let's talk about what happens when this all comes together,"},{"time":737000,"text":"when you tie the three things together."},{"time":739000,"text":"And polio, I think, is one of the most powerful examples."},{"time":743000,"text":"We've seen a 99 percent reduction in polio in 20 years."},{"time":747000,"text":"So if you look back to 1988,"},{"time":749000,"text":"there are about 350,000 cases of polio"},{"time":752000,"text":"on the planet that year."},{"time":754000,"text":"In 2009, we're down to 1,600 cases."},{"time":757000,"text":"Well how did that happen?"},{"time":760000,"text":"Let's look at a country like India."},{"time":762000,"text":"They have over a billion people in this country,"},{"time":765000,"text":"but they have 35,000 local doctors"},{"time":768000,"text":"who report paralysis,"},{"time":770000,"text":"and clinicians, a huge reporting system in chemists."},{"time":773000,"text":"They have two and a half million vaccinators."},{"time":777000,"text":"But let me make the story a little bit more concrete for you."},{"time":779000,"text":"Let me tell you the story of Shriram,"},{"time":781000,"text":"an 18 month boy in Bihar,"},{"time":783000,"text":"a northern state in India."},{"time":785000,"text":"This year on August 8th, he felt paralysis"},{"time":788000,"text":"and on the 13th, his parents took him to the doctor."},{"time":792000,"text":"On August 14th and 15th, they took a stool sample,"},{"time":794000,"text":"and by the 25th of August,"},{"time":796000,"text":"it was confirmed he had Type 1 polio."},{"time":799000,"text":"By August 30th, a genetic test was done,"},{"time":802000,"text":"and we knew what strain of polio Shriram had."}]},{"cues":[{"time":805000,"text":"Now it could have come from one of two places."},{"time":807000,"text":"It could have come from Nepal, just to the north, across the border,"},{"time":810000,"text":"or from Jharkhand, a state just to the south."},{"time":813000,"text":"Luckily, the genetic testing proved"},{"time":816000,"text":"that, in fact, this strand came north,"},{"time":818000,"text":"because, had it come from the south,"},{"time":820000,"text":"it would have had a much wider impact in terms of transmission."},{"time":822000,"text":"So many more people would have been affected."},{"time":824000,"text":"So what's the endgame?"},{"time":826000,"text":"Well on September 4th, there was a huge mop-up campaign,"},{"time":829000,"text":"which is what you do in polio."},{"time":831000,"text":"They went out and where Shriram lives,"},{"time":833000,"text":"they vaccinated two million people."},{"time":835000,"text":"So in less than a month,"},{"time":837000,"text":"we went from one case of paralysis"},{"time":839000,"text":"to a targeted vaccination program."},{"time":842000,"text":"And I'm happy to say only one other person in that area got polio."},{"time":845000,"text":"That's how you keep"},{"time":847000,"text":"a huge outbreak from spreading,"},{"time":849000,"text":"and it shows what can happen"},{"time":851000,"text":"when local people have the data in their hands;"},{"time":854000,"text":"they can save lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":857000,"text":"Now one of the challenges in polio, still, is marketing,"},{"time":860000,"text":"but it might not be what you think."},{"time":862000,"text":"It's not the marketing on the ground."},{"time":864000,"text":"It's not telling the parents,"},{"time":866000,"text":"\"If you see paralysis, take your child to the doctor"},{"time":868000,"text":"or get your child vaccinated.\""},{"time":870000,"text":"We have a problem with marketing in the donor community."},{"time":873000,"text":"The G8 nations have been incredibly generous on polio"},{"time":875000,"text":"over the last 20 years,"},{"time":877000,"text":"but we're starting to have something called polio fatigue"},{"time":880000,"text":"and that is that the donor nations"},{"time":882000,"text":"aren't willing to fund polio any longer."},{"time":884000,"text":"So by next summer, we're sighted to run out of money on polio."},{"time":887000,"text":"So we are 99 percent"},{"time":890000,"text":"of the way there on this goal"},{"time":892000,"text":"and we're about to run short of money."},{"time":895000,"text":"And I think that if the marketing were more aspirational,"},{"time":898000,"text":"if we could focus as a community"},{"time":900000,"text":"on how far we've come"},{"time":902000,"text":"and how amazing it would be"},{"time":904000,"text":"to eradicate this disease,"},{"time":906000,"text":"we could put polio fatigue"},{"time":908000,"text":"and polio behind us."},{"time":910000,"text":"And if we could do that,"},{"time":912000,"text":"we could stop vaccinating everybody, worldwide,"},{"time":914000,"text":"in all of our countries for polio."},{"time":917000,"text":"And it would only be the second disease ever"},{"time":919000,"text":"wiped off the face of the planet."},{"time":922000,"text":"And we are so close."},{"time":924000,"text":"And this victory is so possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":928000,"text":"So if Coke's marketers came to me"},{"time":931000,"text":"and asked me to define happiness,"},{"time":935000,"text":"I'd say my vision of happiness"},{"time":937000,"text":"is a mother holding healthy baby"},{"time":940000,"text":"in her arms."},{"time":942000,"text":"To me, that is deep happiness."},{"time":947000,"text":"And so if we can learn lessons from the innovators in every sector,"},{"time":950000,"text":"then in the future we make together,"},{"time":953000,"text":"that happiness"},{"time":955000,"text":"can be just as ubiquitous"},{"time":957000,"text":"as Coca-Cola."}]},{"cues":[{"time":959000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":961000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}